    // ── Synthèses Tarot ──────────────────────────────────────
    "interpretation.synthesis.tarot.1": "Right now, {kw0} is present in your life. This opens the way for {kw1} to evolve, and what's coming is {kw2}.",
    "interpretation.synthesis.tarot.2": "You start from {kw0}. Step by step, this path leads you toward {kw2}.",
    "interpretation.synthesis.tarot.3": "This reading shows a moment of change. What is shifting in you right now is {kw1}.",
    "interpretation.synthesis.tarot.4": "Three stages: first {kw0} sets the scene. Then {kw1} puts it in motion. And finally {kw2} shows where it's all going.",
    "interpretation.synthesis.tarot.5": "What your cards are showing right now: everything you're going through is preparing you for {kw2}.",
    "interpretation.synthesis.tarot.6": "{kw0} and {kw1} are both present in your life at the same time. It's this combination that creates movement.",
    "interpretation.synthesis.tarot.7": "{kw1} is changing within you. This change is preparing the arrival of {kw2}.",
    "interpretation.synthesis.tarot.8": "You're no longer fully in {kw0}, and not yet fully in {kw2}. You're in between, and that's exactly where everything happens.",
    "interpretation.synthesis.tarot.9": "These three cards tell a single story: a movement that is unfolding in your life right now.",
    "interpretation.synthesis.tarot.10": "This reading points toward {kw2}. It's not far away — it's already beginning.",
    "interpretation.synthesis.tarot.11": "Everything starts from {kw0}. That's your situation today, and it's a good starting point.",
    "interpretation.synthesis.tarot.12": "{kw1} is transforming. And this transformation is exactly what's needed to bring {kw2} forward.",

    // ── Synthèses Anges ──────────────────────────────────────
    "interpretation.synthesis.angels.1": "The angels are guiding you in three steps: letting go of {e0}, receiving {e1}, and becoming {e2}.",
    "interpretation.synthesis.angels.2": "What you're releasing, {e0}, is making room for something new: {e2}.",
    "interpretation.synthesis.angels.3": "{e1} is entering your life right now. It's a response to what you're going through.",
    "interpretation.synthesis.angels.4": "By releasing {e0}, you're opening yourself to {e1}. That's the movement the angels see for you.",
    "interpretation.synthesis.angels.5": "At the end of this path, there is {e2}. That's who you're becoming — not a distant dream.",
    "interpretation.synthesis.angels.6": "{e1} helps you become {e2}. What you're receiving now is preparing who you will be.",
    "interpretation.synthesis.angels.7": "Letting go of {e0} takes courage. But the angels are telling you that you're ready for what comes next.",
    "interpretation.synthesis.angels.8": "You're not alone{genderSuffix} in this moment. A caring presence accompanies your every step.",
    "interpretation.synthesis.angels.9": "Three stages: {e0} settles, {e1} arrives, {e2} takes root. Each step has its place.",
    "interpretation.synthesis.angels.10": "The angels already see {e2} in you. It's already there, growing.",
    "interpretation.synthesis.angels.11": "What you're receiving, {e1}, you made possible yourself. Keep going.",
    "interpretation.synthesis.angels.12": "This reading invites you to trust. Not blindly — but with the certainty that you're on the right path.",

    // ── Actions Tarot ──────────────────────────────────────
    "interpretation.action.tarot.1": "{name}, over the next few days: notice what's really drawing your attention. That's where your energy wants to go.",
    "interpretation.action.tarot.2": "{name}, a simple piece of advice: before making an important decision, ask yourself if it's taking you closer to what you truly want — or further away.",
    "interpretation.action.tarot.3": "{name}, this reading is telling you not to force things. If something is resisting, let it rest. Clarity comes when you stop pushing.",
    "interpretation.action.tarot.4": "{name}, pay attention to the small signs around you this week. They're part of the movement your cards have shown.",
    "interpretation.action.tarot.5": "{name}, the right timing is now. If you wait for the perfect moment, it won't come. Start with what you have.",
    "interpretation.action.tarot.6": "{name}, talk about how you're feeling with someone you trust. Putting it into words will help you move forward.",
    "interpretation.action.tarot.7": "{name}, take care of yourself physically this week. The energy of this reading asks that you stay grounded in your body.",
    "interpretation.action.tarot.8": "{name}, let go of one thing you're trying to control too much right now. That release is exactly what you need.",

    // ── Actions Anges ──────────────────────────────────────
    "interpretation.action.angels.1": "{name}, take 5 quiet minutes today and ask yourself: what have I been carrying for too long? Just naming it is already an act of release.",
    "interpretation.action.angels.2": "{name}, the angels are asking you to stop justifying yourself. You don't need anyone else's permission to move forward.",
    "interpretation.action.angels.3": "{name}, do something kind for yourself today — something you've been putting off for weeks. That's the message.",
    "interpretation.action.angels.4": "{name}, observe without judging this week. Something you keep noticing around you is a sign. Trust it.",
    "interpretation.action.angels.5": "{name}, say yes to something you usually refuse out of fear. The angels are telling you this moment is safe.",
    "interpretation.action.angels.6": "{name}, write down what you're feeling. Not for anyone else — just for you. It releases what can't come out any other way.",
    "interpretation.action.angels.7": "{name}, find beauty in one ordinary thing today. It's a simple practice that shifts the energy around you.",
    "interpretation.action.angels.8": "{name}, when someone asks how you're doing, answer honestly. Don't just say 'fine'. That honesty is a spiritual act.",

